reviewText: Great seller! Easy transaction! Excellent!  Highly recommended. Thank you!
I received the VHS quickly and it was in good condition. My great grandson loves Barney. I wish I could find more Barney items for him.

My daughters enjoy Barney (they are 1 and 2.5 years old).  They enjoy the music and dancing and sing and dance along as best they can.  They love the Barney, Baby Bop and Bj and all the fun things that they do.  This is a wonderful video to teach the seasons although a little hard for them to completely understand the concept as we don't have snow where we live.  Barney fans will not be disappointed.
